defaultThe challenge for the UK’s implementing authorities will be to implement the new CAP framework so that it adequately supports and drives farmers and land mangers to address long standing environment
defaultal
default problems.  For 
defaultcomplex environmental challenges complex responses are often required however this does not mean that the interface with farmers and land managers has to be complicated. Indeed we would support as user-friendly a system as possible but it is vital to recog
defaultnise that in order to secure effectiveness in outcomes, intelligently designed and evidence based systems of delivery will be required
default.
